Office Conversions:
sudo apt-get install openoffice.org openoffice.org-headless openoffice.org-writer openoffice.org-draw openoffice.org-calc python-uno
soffice -headless -nofirststartwizard -accept="socket,host=localhost,port=8100;urp;"
killall -9 soffice.bin

xps Conversions:
sudo apt-get install libxext-dev libxt-dev
wget "http://downloads.ghostscript.com/public/ghostpdl-9.05.tar.bz2"
tar xjf ./ghostpdl-9.05.tar.gz
cd ghostpdl-9.05/
./configure
make xps
cp ./xps/obj/gxps /usr/bin
gxps -dNOPAUSE -dBATCH -sDEVICE=pdfwrite -r150 -o outfile infile

@todo: move to conditional imports of dependency packages. Lots of installs do not need all the dependencies but 
